summary: Make Skyrim's UI sound like good 'ol nostalgic Oblivon's.
descriptionHtml:
This simply makes Skyrim's UI sound like good 'ol nostalgic Oblivon's.

This is modular with NMM so you can choose what sounds you want installed. There's also alternate nullifying options if you'd rather have a certain sound silenced.
author: ModelsOfBoats
